== 潛在續集與跨界 ==
《科學怪人：屠魔大戰》因票房及評價不如預期，使得續集幾乎不可能推出。「{{link-en|決戰異世界系列電影|Underworld (film series)}}」的創作者[[凱文·格雷維奧斯|凱文·格雷維奧斯]]在此前曾表示，他打算讓《科學怪人：屠魔大戰》與《決戰異世界》作跨界合作。格雷維奧斯在採訪時透露，在他劇本的初稿中，由[[凱特·貝琴薩|凱特·貝琴薩]]飾演的{{link-en|莎倫娜 (決戰異世界)|Selene (Underworld)|莎倫娜}}將現身於片尾片段，且還包含有與《決戰異世界》相關的[[彩蛋_(媒体)|彩蛋]]，但後來並未採用<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.iamrogue.com/news/interviews/item/10516-iar-exclusive-interview-kevin-grevioux-talks-i-frankenstein-a-possible-sequel-and-crossover-with-the-underworld-franchise.html| title=IAR Exclusive Interview: Kevin Grevioux  Talks ''I, Frankenstein'', A Possible Sequel and Crossover with the 'Underworld' Franchise| last1=Philbick| first1=Jami| date=January 21, 2014| website=I Am Rogue.com| publisher=[[Rogue_(company)|Rogue]]| accessdate=February 28, 2014| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320042231/http://www.iamrogue.com/news/interviews/item/10516-iar-exclusive-interview-kevin-grevioux-talks-i-frankenstein-a-possible-sequel-and-crossover-with-the-underworld-franchise.html| archive-date=2016-03-20| dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

